des: Every morning and afternoon, Room to Breathe by Juniper Row Wellness offers notes of inspiration and focus to help keep your emotions grounded, your mind clear, and your attention anchored in the moment. It is our hope to nudge you in the direction you desire for yourself, even when distractions and discouragements get in the way. You can do this! And Room to Breathe by Juniper Row Wellness can help.
